WEBVTT

00:00.512 --> 00:01.913
<i>Previously...on Legend
of the Seeker</i>

00:02.776 --> 00:04.577
<i>You have to take the Stone
of Tears</i>

00:04.578 --> 00:07.513
<i>to the Pillars of Creation on the
day of the summer solstice,</i>

00:07.692 --> 00:09.258
<i>and repair the tear in the veil.</i>

00:09.259 --> 00:12.229
What do you want?
The same as you, dear brother.

00:12.230 --> 00:13.597
To save the world.

00:13.598 --> 00:16.366
If you help me achieve
this victory for him,

00:16.367 --> 00:18.738
I have no doubt that the
Keeper will reward you

00:18.739 --> 00:21.509
beyond imagining.

00:21.510 --> 00:22.944
<i>Whoever gains possession</i>

00:22.945 --> 00:26.011
<i>of all three Boxes of Orden</i>
<i>will be unstoppable.</i>

00:26.012 --> 00:28.977
<i>She is pristinely ungifted.</i>

00:28.978 --> 00:33.077
Magic doesn't work on me.
Not evenen the magic of Orden.

00:33.078 --> 00:34.613
The true Lord Rahl is in danger.

00:34.614 --> 00:35.847
I need your help to save him.

00:35.848 --> 00:37.115
Do you think we can trust her?

00:37.116 --> 00:38.516
I've known her for a long time.

00:38.517 --> 00:41.987
You once swore to kill
the man you now serve.

00:41.988 --> 00:43.622
Why did you lie to me?

00:43.623 --> 00:45.858
I want you back on my side.

00:45.859 --> 00:49.694
<i>Fortunately, I knew of your special
friendship with Dahlia</i>

00:49.695 --> 00:52.530
<i>The Agiel's touch will be more
painful to her</i>

00:52.531 --> 00:54.632
<i>than all the fires of the Underworld.</i>

00:57.103 --> 00:58.670
Cara, why?

00:58.671 --> 01:00.471
I brought what you asked for.

01:04.441 --> 01:09.277
<i>Richard Cypher, you are the
true Seeker.</i>

