01:25.930 --> 01:29.299
Rahl is taking the Stone
of Tears northeast.

01:29.300 --> 01:31.602
The Pillars of Creation
are to the south.

01:31.603 --> 01:33.837
Rahl isn't taking the
Stone to the Pillars.

01:33.838 --> 01:36.272
He has no intention of
using it to seal the veil.

01:36.273 --> 01:39.007
Then where's he taking it?

01:47.217 --> 01:49.952
Why are we stopping?

01:49.953 --> 01:55.121
Marianna, do you really fail to
grasp the import of the moment?

01:55.122 --> 01:58.091
We are about to deliver
the Stone of Tears

01:58.092 --> 02:00.059
to the Keeper.

02:00.060 --> 02:04.497
And once he has it, the tear in
the veil can never be sealed,

02:04.498 --> 02:06.699
and the World of the Living

02:06.700 --> 02:10.202
will fall forever into darkness.

02:10.203 --> 02:13.939
But before we proceed
into the rift,

02:13.940 --> 02:17.843
let us offer a prayer of
gratitude to our master

02:17.844 --> 02:21.045
for allowing us,
his humble servants,

02:21.046 --> 02:23.881
a small part to play

02:23.882 --> 02:27.017
in his glorious victory.

